{"tid":1276754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者朋友幫幫手","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:21:19.000Z","uid":254517,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c733db1febf3c7a7861100b02cd41a84539bd3fe","tid":1276754,"uid":254517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"狗官陸續會開啲唔知直播定重播嘅垃圾記招<br />\n然後又講埋啲廢話<br />\n可唔可以幫手不停問：<span style=\"color: red;\">動機係咩</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: blue;\">示威者企圖衝撞我地警方防線</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: red;\">咁佢地嘅動機係咩？</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: blue;\">示威者企圖衝入垃圾會</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: red;\">咁佢地衝入垃圾會動機係咩？</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: blue;\">示威者想破壞垃圾會</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: red;\">咁佢哋破壞垃圾會嘅動機又係咩？</span><br />\n<br />\n問撚到佢一係答反送中一係答I can't find a word<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地(唔包括垃圾TVB) 無咗你地午夜更黑暗<br />\n<br />\n最後 對唔住 我發夢傳咗兩個鐘物資 聽到清場我決定離開 係我怕事 係我淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想比人拉 都唔希望大家有事 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不流血 不受傷 不被捕</span></span>"},{"pid":"7257f6b941a14610c09be56dc4eed50d683746a9","tid":1276754,"uid":254517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b03118b8e98c4a5e6a7dd8a46bd16501d9821710","tid":1276754,"uid":254517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edf677a8b4f352e1bce67818a6b45b959eb29c83","tid":1276754,"uid":254517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:42:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd2fe66d09effccbeba253